beginning; containing an area of Two Thousand Ninety Three (2,093) square meters, more or less. All points referred to are indicated on the plan and are marked on the ground by P.S. Cyl. conc. mons. 15 x 60 cm., bearings true; declination 0 deg. 50′ E., date of original survey, April 8, 1920 — February 21, 1921 and that of the subdivision survey, May 5-22, 1969″

IN WITNESS THEREOF , I have hereunto set my hand and cause the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed hereto.

Done in the City of Manila, this 25th day of August in the year of our Lord, Two Thousand and Five.

(Sgd.) GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO

By the President: (Sgd.) EDUARDO R. ERMITA Executive Secretary

